parameters: *splash*
*splash*
*splash*
The sound of the waves that come and go tickles my ears.

The smell of the sea is loudly proclaiming, it's the
ocean!
We took about a 3 hour car drive.
Then hopped on a boat for an hour.

The journey was so long that I wondered how far we were
going.

This place that seems to make both my heart and body
soaking wet, is a deserted island get-away.

I don't know who planned it, but having a 2-night, 3-day
training camp in a place like this...
They have my respect.
Isn't this the perfect chance to get a girlfriend?
I looked around with hopeful eyes.
kanae (1)
Kanae

Ah, what are you doing, Hikaru! Hurry up and put down your
bags, lets go to the sea!
saruyama (1)
Saruyama
Leave me alone. I'm having weird fantasies right now.
akane (1)
Akane
Ahaha, Hikaru, you have a weird face!
renka (1)
Renka
Oh, really. They look just like Saruyama-sama.
tsugumi (1)
Tsugumi
I looked around... and...
It seems that there is no one here to accompany me.

I walked dejectedly to the changing room, leaving my bag
behind in a random place.
Ah, I wonder where my girlfriend is.
kanae (1)
Kanae.

She and I are childhood friends who attended the same
elementary and middle school.

In high school, we had a little misunderstanding, but in
the end, we ended up going to the same university and
our long-standing bad relationship continues.

They have a rough personality and often resort to violence,
but they seem to be generally cheerful and quite
popular.

It seems like she's never been in a relationship with
anyone before, but well, from her perspective I think
she has plenty of options.
tsugumi (1)
Tsugumi.

I heard that she has been friends with Kanae since high
school.
I don't have much experience talking with them, but...

They seem to have become a famous person in our department,
with her doll-like features and cold personality.

They usually wear clothes with little exposure, but I'm
looking forward to seeing them in a swimsuit during
this training camp.
akane (1)
Akane.

For some reason, among the many members in our sports
club, I think Akane stands out the most.

I heard that they entered the school as a swimming
scholarship student, but for some reason, they joined
the Mystery Club, which is a mysterious choice.
And, most importantly...
Her chest, her chest is incredibly large.

Are those watermelons, or perhaps cantaloupes...  She
looks like a Cerberus with three heads.
renka (1)
Renka.

Recently, they joined the club as a new student, but they have a
strange atmosphere like a fourth-dimensional girl.

Sometimes they say things that don't make sense, and I can't
even understand what they're thinking...

They're kind and cute, but for some reason, it seems like
they're struggling in their studies.

If a girl like this were my girlfriend, I would shower
them with lots of love.
They really have no sense of the world.
saruyama (1)
Saruyama.
This is just a wild monkey.
saruyama (2)
Saruyama
Hey, did you just think of something rude just now?

From the way they suddenly get angry, it seems like they
have no self-control.
saruyama (3)
Saruyama
I've completely forgotten what I was thinking!
taiyou (1)
Taiyou
Surprisingly, the place isn't bad.
Taiyou
Hey~ The pier was really old and rough.
kenta (1)
Kenta
They're quick~ I guess it's because they're young. Oop...
This delinquent-like guy is Taiyou.

They're a senior in the first grade and also the president of
our club.

Originally, they were involved in sports activities, but it
seems like they joined this club after retiring due to an
injury.

However, now they seem completely lively and
full of life.

Despite how they look, they are surprisingly a responsible and
good senior.
And over there, the person with the big body is Kenta.

Every day they say things that make them sound like an old
man, but they're only one year older than me.

Originally, him and Taiyou-senpai were from the same club, it
seems like they left the club together when Taiyou-
senpai retired.

They have a good personality that matches their imposing
figure, and they're like the big brother of our club.
...anyway

It's a shame that some club members didn't come, but if we
can have fun with just us, then it's okay.

Maybe there's a possibility of some slightly naughty events
happening during the training camp.

From now on, I will spend the next two nights and three
days living in a training camp with that excited
feeling.
However...
Surprisingly, the final night arrived without anything happening.
Hikaru
The plan didn't go as expected, did it...
Saruyama
They're not the type to despair alone. It's just like Hikaru.
